where, n is the rotational speed; D is the impeller diameter (m), with a maximum value of 0.078 m based on reactor geometry; 

    ρ

 is the liquid density, taken as 1 g·cm-3 for the wastewater; and Np is the power number of the impeller, which is 0.696 for the selected impeller type. Substitution of these parameters yields a stirring power of approximately 0.55 kW.
